Holiday greetings all.  I have a lot of 20 freshly graded T206's for sale.  Would prefer to sell as a lot so we'll see what happens for a day or two before listing the cards for individual sale.  Asking $1100/bo for the lot, which includes free insured priority mail shipping with signature confirmation in continental US.  Payment via personal check, money orders and Paypal (please add 3%). You may contact me at mcantista@juno.com. Thanks everyone.  List and scans below.
